  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>RepairQ offers opportunity management for Contacts (leads), Customers, Quotes, and Appointments. Users can easily create quotes that can be printed, emailed, and converted into tickets.</p><p>A quote has all of the features of a standard ticket with a few key differences:</p><ul><li><p>Inventory is not pulled nor consumed for a quote.</p></li><li><p>Quotes are not included in revenue reports.</p></li><li><p>Quotes do not require a transaction to close out the ticket.</p></li></ul><p>Quotes also use the same status system that you use for tickets and repairs. Converting a quote into an active ticket is a one-click process, and once converted, the related inventory is immediately pulled to the ticket.</p><h3 id=\"Quotes:ConvertaQuoteintoaTicket-AdditionalResources\">Additional Resources</h3><ul><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1933246809\" rel=\"nofollow\">RepairQ Opportunities (Quotes)</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1934458927\" rel=\"nofollow\">Contacts Overview</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/2022080562\" rel=\"nofollow\">Quotes: Save a Ticket as a Quote</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1934917634\" rel=\"nofollow\">Quotes: Convert a Quote to a Ticket</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1934491696/Appointments\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1934491696\" data-linked-resource-version=\"6\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Appointment Resources</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1933246465\" rel=\"nofollow\">Automated Notification Resources</a></p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1934917634/image-20230622-175153.png?api=v2\"></span><h2 id=\"Quotes:ConvertaQuoteintoaTicket-ConvertaQuotetoaTicket\">Convert a Quote to a Ticket</h2><p /><p>On the Navigation Bar, go to <strong>Opportunities</strong> \u2192 <strong>Quotes</strong>. Use the filters to locate the quote that you would like to convert. Next to the quote, click the <strong>Options button (\u22ee)</strong> under the Actions column.  From the list of options, click <strong>Convert</strong>.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" width=\"760\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1934917634/image-20230622-175157.png?api=v2\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1934917634/image-20230622-175200.png?api=v2\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" width=\"199\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1934917634/image-20230622-175203.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>The quote will convert to a ticket, and any pending inventory will be pulled from stock. You can save the ticket if you need to make changes at a later date or continue with the regular ticket workflow.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1934917634/image-20230622-175207.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p /><p>START 1.22.X</p>",
